{"type": "article", "id": 13315, "title": "水泥小妖", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122453W5HKo4v1hsDckbP3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t《捉妖记》的大卖让很多人爱上了胡巴小妖，最近，韩国设计公司 Hobby Design 也推出了一套小妖的玩偶，虽然不是胡巴，但是内容之丰富，形态之可爱，一点也不输给那个白萝卜哦。这些“小妖”都适用水泥材料做成，包括玩偶，烛台，贴纸，纹身等一系列产品。“小妖”们有不同的名字和形态，给人以充分的想像力发挥空间，感觉可以蹲在家里玩儿整整一天。这是购买链接。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122448cD8WeAFu7EGJCZk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122448xerSTW6BV9CqIYPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122448mwlEvaoSU76HFfCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122449Uve8lpd0cuawOFEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122449jxWOvkFoYlhMqbJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122450m3dGl4WHUpgrBx7K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122451WxLvai21tHk59D4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122451V2z1ZPeHBGciAr0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122452kV7L0YxeA1Zh9Hbn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}